---
---

<section class="story section" id="story">
  <div class="container story__grid">
    <div class="story__media reveal" data-clip>
      <img src="/images/portrait.jpg" loading="lazy" alt="A roaster at work" />
      <span class="reveal__cover"></span>
      <span class="story__badge">Est. 2019</span>
    </div>

    <div class="story__text">
      <p class="eyebrow" data-reveal>Our story</p>
      <h2 class="story__title" data-split>Roasted by hand, by ear, by nose</h2>
      <p data-reveal>
        We started Ember with one cast-iron drum and a stubborn belief: that
        coffee tastes best when someone is paying attention. Every batch is
        roasted by hand — never by autopilot.
      </p>
      <p data-reveal>
        We buy seasonally, in small lots, straight from farms we&apos;ve sat
        down with. What lands in your cup was green a few weeks ago and roasted
        a few days back.
      </p>
      <a href="#ritual" class="btn btn--ghost" data-reveal>How we roast</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
  .story {
    background: var(--void);
  }

  .story__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .story__media {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;

    img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
    }
  }

  .reveal__cover {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: var(--coal);
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .story__badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: 1.1rem;
    left: 1.1rem;
    z-index: 3;
    background: var(--amber);
    color: var(--void);
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.45rem 0.9rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
  }

  .story__title {
    font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 4.6vw, 3.6rem);
    margin: 0.9rem 0 1.6rem;
    max-width: 14ch;
  }

  .story__text p {
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
    max-width: 34rem;
  }

  .story__text .btn {
    margin-top: 0.8rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .story__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .story__media {
      aspect-ratio: 16 / 11;
    }
  }
</style>
